          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "bc940d0fb3c4",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": "5. "
            },
            {
              "_key": "69b30ecb36a1",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [
                "strong"
              ],
              "text": "Supports Premium Pricing"
            }
          ],
          "markDefs": [],
          "style": "h3"
        },
        {
          "_key": "d6c738e75284",
          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "f5a5883c3e72",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": "Experiences sold through storytelling are "
            },
            {
              "_key": "923cd75a445c",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [
                "strong"
              ],
              "text": "perceived as more valuable"
            },
            {
              "_key": "5fc7334cae44",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": ". Guests aren‚Äôt just paying for a night‚Äôs stay‚Äîthey‚Äôre paying for the memory, the atmosphere, and the ‚Äúexperience narrative‚Äù you provide. This allows hospitality brands to justify higher prices."
            }
          ],
          "markDefs": [],
          "style": "normal"
        },
        {
          "_key": "63562fec14a2",
          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "bb53403c0755",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": "6. "
            },
            {
              "_key": "8bffd744c009",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [
                "strong"
              ],
              "text": "Builds Trust and Authenticity"
            }
          ],
          "markDefs": [],
          "style": "h3"
        },
        {
          "_key": "140c7f1c9cdc",
          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "b44c043467b7",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": "Authentic stories about local culture, sustainability, or personal staff experiences build credibility. Guests feel your brand is "
            },
            {
              "_key": "6631857f2459",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [
                "strong"
              ],
              "text": "real and relatable"
            },
            {
              "_key": "b44f0b1a50a1",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": ", not just transactional."
            }
          ],
          "markDefs": [],
          "style": "normal"
        },
        {
          "_key": "a39724459580",
          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "f833348bb794",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [
                "strong"
              ],
              "text": "Bottom line:"
            },
            {
              "_key": "61f50527e7e9",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": " Without storytelling, a hotel or restaurant risks being just another option in a search engine. With storytelling, it becomes "
