      "body": [
        {
          "_key": "830a0950e5a8",
          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "183ef4de23d8",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [
                "strong"
              ],
              "text": "Hospitality storytelling in marketing"
            },
            {
              "_key": "26b2097d83f7",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": " is the practice of using narrative techniques to promote hotels, restaurants, resorts, or travel experiences in a way that emotionally engages potential guests. Instead of just listing amenities or services, brands craft stories that highlight experiences, values, culture, or unique moments that a guest can have. It‚Äôs about selling "
            },
            {
              "_key": "8f06605c4cb7",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [
                "strong"
              ],
              "text": "feelings, memories, and lifestyle"
            },
            {
              "_key": "364d809c4f23",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": ", not just a room or meal."
            }
          ],
          "markDefs": [],
          "style": "normal"
        },
        {
          "_key": "332afa28e110",
          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "4e8cb9f5378b",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": "1. "
            },
            {
              "_key": "643496a01231",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [
                "strong"
              ],
              "text": "Focus on Guest Experience"
            }
          ],
          "markDefs": [],
          "style": "h3"
        },
        {
          "_key": "da8afed12c28",
          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "a3a11319feb8",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": "Rather than saying ‚Äúwe have a pool and spa,‚Äù hospitality storytelling might describe a couple enjoying a sunrise yoga session on a rooftop deck or a family sharing a candlelit dinner in a cozy restaurant. The goal is to "
            },
            {
              "_key": "a0fd039af899",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [
                "strong"
              ],
              "text": "transport the audience into the experience"
            },
            {
              "_key": "0507973fe7e7",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": "."
            }
          ],
          "markDefs": [],
          "style": "normal"
        },
        {
          "_key": "21d09c8c3694",
          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "e6280df99f69",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": "2. "
            },
            {
              "_key": "5f5179d44d50",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [
                "strong"
              ],
              "text": "Highlight Unique Brand Personality"
            }
          ],
          "markDefs": [],
          "style": "h3"
        },
        {
          "_key": "aa7a33dbf5b5",
          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "56d1dee34a01",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": "Every hotel, resort, or restaurant has its own character. Storytelling emphasizes what makes a brand different:"
            }
          ],
          "markDefs": [],
          "style": "normal"
        },
        {
          "_key": "19cff367c655",
          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "40c4abdfdf55",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": "Local culture and traditions"
            }
          ],
          "level": 1,
          "listItem": "bullet",
          "markDefs": [],
          "style": "normal"
        },
        {
          "_key": "10748636fb73",
          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "cc06be44e80c",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": "Design and ambiance"
            }
          ],
          "level": 1,
          "listItem": "bullet",
          "markDefs": [],
          "style": "normal"
        },
        {
          "_key": "c33cbb5fc99a",
          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "07668acabaaa",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": "Sustainable or ethical practices"
